Version 0.2.1 -> 0.2.2
======================

- header file "use_daqmx.h" is now included, thus this
  toolbox works with NI-DAQmx Base 2.x/3.x OR NI-DAQmx 8.x/9.x
- use pre-built help pages to circumvent minor but annoying
  building problems
- cleanup of builder/loader scripts

Version 0.2 -> 0.2.1
====================

- tiny fix for compilation with ScicosLab 4.3

Changes Version 0.1 -> 0.2
==========================

- all functions of NI-DAQmx C API are now interfaced
. bug in DAQ_CfgInputBuffer fixed 
- example pulseWidth.sce added
